      "message": "Status should remain simple and have limited values. Once Draft is eliminated, we have a nice simple status model:\n\nInitial status: New\nNew: can be Merged or Abandoned\nAbandoned: can be restored to New\nMerged: permanent end state\n\nIf we add WIP to the mix, the model gets complicated:\n\nInitial status: New or WIP\nNew: can be WIP, Merged, or Abandoned\nWIP: can be New or Abandoned\nAbandoned: can be restored to New or WIP, depending on previous value of status\nMerged: permanent end state",
